REST API for Sentiment Analysis

This workflow showcases the Rest API capabilities of the KNIME Server. We are reusing the model trained on the airline reviews and providing sentiment analyis as a service.

Please try our corresponding responsive, mobile ready application to see sentiment prediction in action.
